#ad  So of course we filmed the whole process of making our AC Valhalla cosplays.

Today I have the bracer video for you. The whole thing is entirely made of foam and fake fur. You can also see how we go all the way to make EVA foam from @cosplayshop.be look like leather. See? It’s no magic! Just a little spraypaint, a little rolling of the foam and the right paintjob. We really liked to make these bracers because there are so many different details and techniques involved.

Guys, I’m happy!
This weekend I’ll be at the first convention after 18 months. It will be outside (it’s a convention-festival-concert-mix) and the Covid safety regulations are good. 
God I missed it so much. After such a long time it will feel kinda weird to be around some more people but the good old convention vibes will kick in soon enough and I will enjoy every single minute of it. And of course much more than before. 
I’m sooo looking forward to meet many of you. ☺️☺️☺️ 
See you at @elbenwald_festival this weekend.

node.text:
Sometimes (actually pretty often these days) heroes  don’t wear capes!!! (or two swords 😉)
Big shoutout to all the rescue workers who worked their butts off to save people‘s lives, homes or pets in the big flood here in my hometown and a huuuuge area around it. Some died doing it. 😞 
To be honest it feels great that there are many true heroes around us in our daily lives. If everything is fine we don’t see them. But when sth bad happens they are there to help. 

Now I’m super impressed. I never experienced sth like this. 

Hearing the fire truck sirens all day long, day and night, knowing that they are out there helping and risking their lives without a break changed my mind a lot in many ways. Too many to tell you all of them. But the most important one is that I’m super thankful. 
Thank you rescue workers!!! All of you are true heroes!!!

Pic of course by @eosandy_ best corgi by @annacremer.x

Was gibt’s Besseres als in der Badewanne The Witcher 3 zu zocken? Egal wo ihr seid: Mit PS Now erhaltet ihr auf jeden Fall ab sofort Zugriff auf dieses epische Abenteuer!
 
Ob Action-Adventure, Shooter, Horror, Indie oder Rollenspiele: Bei PS Now von @playstationde findet ihr hunderte Games und es kommen jeden Monat neue hinzu! Auf PS4 und PS5 könnt ihr die Games streamen oder downloaden und offline zocken. Aber auch mit einem Windows-PC habt ihr Zugriff auf die PS Now-Bibliothek und könnt Spiele wie Bloodborne, Until Dawn oder God of War streamen.
 
 
What could be better than playing The Witcher 3 in the bathtub? No matter where you are, PS Now gives you access to this epic adventure!
